<span class='line-number'>32</span>
<span class='line-number'>33</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='sh'><span class='line'>&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;!/bin/bash&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;See installed locales <span class="o">(</span><span class="k">for</span> user<span class="o">)</span>.&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;locale&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;You need root rights.&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;su&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;See actually configured locales <span class="k">for</span> root&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;locale&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;See configured locales <span class="k">for</span> system&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;localectl&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;Install locales&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;For <span class="nb">time </span>format close to ISO <span class="m">8601</span> install <span class="p">&amp;</span>lsquo<span class="p">;</span>en_DK<span class="p">&amp;</span>rsquo<span class="p">;</span>.&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;yum langinstall en_US
</span><span class='line'>yum langinstall en_DK
</span><span class='line'>yum langinstall de_DE&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;Edit your locales file.&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;Attention: If you <span class="nb">set </span>LC_ALL variable, it will overwrite all other options.&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;nano /etc/locale.conf
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></p>

<p>Nun ein logout und ein login und die Einstellungen sind wirksam. Unten ist eine Beispieldatei für eine locale abgebildet. Achtung: Wird die LC_ALL-Variable gesetzt, so überschreibt diese alle anderen Einstellungen, egal ob sie danach getätigt werden.
