</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='sh'><span class='line'>&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;Example /etc/locale.conf file.&lt;/h1&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;p&gt;#&lt;/p&gt;
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>&lt;h1&gt;LC_ALL overrides all other locale variables&lt;/h1&gt;
